This library demonstrates how to benchmark user's MPI functions. 

1. Build user library.

  make
  
2. Edit Makefile.inc in top level directory of MPIPerf and setup
   USERLIB_FLAG variable. For example:
   
   USERLIB_FLAGS := -L $(topdir)/examples/usermpi -l usermpi
   
3. Clean and build MPIPerf.

  make clean
  make
  
   
   